FBIS4-38902 "drsov107_m_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-107 Daily Report 3 Jun 1994 Tajikistan Russian Border Guards Kill Russian Border Guards Kill Cross-Border Invaders LD0306082894 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0651 GMT 3 Jun 94 LD0306082894 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [Report by ITAR-TASS correspondent Galina Gridneva] [Text] Dushanbe 3 June TASS -- The border troops on the Tajik-Afghan border last night had to open artillery fire at a group of transgressors who were trying to penetrate the Tajik territory from Afghanistan across the river. All the invaders were killed, according to the Command of the Russian border troops in Tajikistan. No Russian servicemen were killed or wounded.
